sentences.sentence: I suspect that some experts in the field will be keen to address alternative explanations, such as unassessed variables playing a role in the wellbeing decline.
sentences.translation: 我怀疑该领域的一些专家会热衷于寻找其他解释，比如未评估的变量在幸福感下降中发挥的作用。
